{"tid":1406164,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[東鐵]又係時係拖喼反工啦","createTime":"2019-08-04T12:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T12:36:07.000Z","uid":246676,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9b249bbc8c641e0598d7fa0c196508966114d3ab","tid":1406164,"uid":246676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:25:11.000Z","msg":"所以話我強烈譴責咗東鐵好耐<br />\n<br />\n死都唔比錢加幕門<br />\n<br />\n條罅又鬼咁闊<br />\n<br />\n而家大鑊啦<br />\n<br />\n抵死啦<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;分隔線&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n大家反工咁累<br />\n<br />\n又想換新喼<br />\n<br />\n又想感受旅遊氣氛<br />\n<br />\n或者放工要買大量用品既東鐵朋友<br />\n<br />\n係時候拖喼拖手拉車返工啦<br />\n<br />\n聽日記得準時等車<br />\n<br />\n兩手拎手機<br />\n<br />\n再黎人多又推撞<br />\n<br />\n跌野落路軌就咁就會發生<br />\n<br />\n到時記得一齊譴責港鐵<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記住<br />\n<br />\n跌野個責任<br />\n<br />\n係港鐵做唔到野<br />\n<br />\n妄顧乘客及其財產安全</span></span>"},{"pid":"b54079bd8650e6c2137d30b81fe591278c0f7d69","tid":1406164,"uid":246676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:25:56.000Z","msg":"拖喼！"},{"pid":"58553bf14ba728478b4a4240b6ecb0752fa91f06","tid":1406164,"uid":246676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:26:07.000Z","msg":"拖喼！"},{"pid":"29c8f9d5f4b23b9ddfd8a007f93dd229db58ebe2","tid":1406164,"uid":246676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:26:17.000Z","msg":"拖喼！"},{"pid":"fc92fb25261c3009dc57b4f26dc09f8fabc63fbb","tid":1406164,"uid":246676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:26:27.000Z","msg":"拖喼！"},{"pid":"5290725b89210590ed697f2b93f13a66a4bf1b7e","tid":1406164,"uid":246676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:26:38.000Z","msg":"拖喼！"},{"pid":"5b596855a9a0980c5b772227c7d5f1ea6d026921","tid":1406164,"uid":246676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re